{"tid":1990191,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"反對發「免疫通行證」世衛：有抗體不保證不會二次感染","createTime":"2020-04-26T13:30:56.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-26T14:43:00.000Z","uid":81228,"like":0,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"5837d2cd5fe1e5970e6ddc58031e91d777aac153","tid":1990191,"uid":81228,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-26T13:30:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://d2e7nuz2r6mjca.cloudfront.net/2020/4/1587893849_oZ-1280w.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fd2e7nuz2r6mjca.cloudfront.net%2F2020%2F4%2F1587893849_oZ-1280w.jpg&h=98a43df7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n不少國家希望在新冠肺炎疫情有放緩跡象下，重啟經濟活動，並計劃發放「免疫通行證」(Immunity Passport)予證實已對病毒產生抗體的康復人士，令他們可以立即重回工作崗位。<br />\n<br />\n不過，世界衞生組織表示，目前仍然未有證據顯示，新冠肺炎康復者不會受到二次感染。世衛認為，大多數研究顯示，康復者體內雖擁有抗體，但部份人血液中的抗體水平非常低，至今亦未有關於病毒抗體，是否可賦予人類免疫力的研究。<br />\n<br />\n世衛又稱，如擁有抗體的民眾以為不會受到「二次感染」，從而忽視公共衛生及防疫建議，反而有可能增加病毒繼續傳播的風險。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.am730.com.hk/news/%E6%96%B0%E8%81%9E/%e3%80%90%e6%96%b0%e5%86%a0%e8%82%ba%e7%82%8e%e3%80%91%e5%8f%8d%e5%b0%8d%e7%99%bc%e3%80%8c%e5%85%8d%e7%96%ab%e9%80%9a%e8%a1%8c%e8%ad%89%e3%80%8d-%e4%b8%96%e8%a1%9b%ef%bc%9a%e6%9c%89%e6%8a%97%e9%ab%94%e4%b8%8d%e4%bf%9d%e8%ad%89%e4%b8%8d%e6%9c%83%e4%ba%8c%e6%ac%a1%e6%84%9f%e6%9f%93-216519\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.am730.com.hk%2Fnews%2F%25E6%2596%25B0%25E8%2581%259E%2F%25e3%2580%2590%25e6%2596%25b0%25e5%2586%25a0%25e8%2582%25ba%25e7%2582%258e%25e3%2580%2591%25e5%258f%258d%25e5%25b0%258d%25e7%2599%25bc%25e3%2580%258c%25e5%2585%258d%25e7%2596%25ab%25e9%2580%259a%25e8%25a1%258c%25e8%25ad%2589%25e3%2580%258d-%25e4%25b8%2596%25e8%25a1%259b%25ef%25bc%259a%25e6%259c%2589%25e6%258a%2597%25e9%25ab%2594%25e4%25b8%258d%25e4%25bf%259d%25e8%25ad%2589%25e4%25b8%258d%25e6%259c%2583%25e4%25ba%258c%25e6%25ac%25a1%25e6%2584%259f%25e6%259f%2593-216519&d=LcLc405txlysKZNFfpEZ4PilxGv0e2UEk%2F7kpEYl8nk%3D&h=780aa177\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.am730.com.hk/news/%E6%96%B0%E8%81%9E/%e3%80%90%e6%96%b0%e5%86%a0%e8%82%ba%e7%82%8e%e3%80%91%e5%8f%8d%e5%b0%8d%e7%99%bc%e3%80%8c%e5%85%8d%e7%96%ab%e9%80%9a%e8%a1%8c%e8%ad%89%e3%80%8d-%e4%b8%96%e8%a1%9b%ef%bc%9a%e6%9c%89%e6%8a%97%e9%ab%94%e4%b8%8d%e4%bf%9d%e8%ad%89%e4%b8%8d%e6%9c%83%e4%ba%8c%e6%ac%a1%e6%84%9f%e6%9f%93-216519</a>"},{"pid":"e98fa7e3df80914b2f9fd15458af51653aec418c","tid":1990191,"uid":33874,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-26T13:34:50.000Z","msg":"下<br />\n有無抗體啲防疫指示都無人理架啦"},{"pid":"a63bf802db2bf3dc958416f2a271f1b54f62fb20","tid":1990191,"uid":54959,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-26T13:36:45.000Z","msg":"咁我發個宇宙通行證俾你"},{"pid":"40eb01d288f34aca3f24fd8adab6febbf42ee3e4","tid":1990191,"uid":290883,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-26T13:42:42.000Z","msg":"咁夠膽 屌支共？"},{"pid":"30d41b993ce38c394b28c9af0d13d5e7781106df","tid":1990191,"uid":196329,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a63bf802db2bf3dc958416f2a271f1b54f62fb20","tid":1990191,"uid":54959,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-26T13:36:45.000Z","msg":"咁我發個宇宙通行證俾你"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-26T14:43:00.000Z","msg":"我都即刻諗到呢個<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}